5%259C%258B%25E9%259B%2584&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK610Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=f85f4071\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E8%B6%99%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%84</a><br />\n<br />\n趙國雄早年畢業於天主教新民書院以及曾在香港浸會大學修讀社會學和經濟學。<span style=\"color: red;\">在學期間</span>與已故香港大學學生會會長陳毓祥爭取捉拿前總警司葛柏而上街示威，最終<span style=\"color: red;\">被英國殖民政府控以「非法遊行」及「非法集會」而留下案底及判守行為兩年</span>。<br />\n<br />\n只要有料既話, 即使有案底, 阿李生都請</blockquote><br />\n今次係直情入去坐過幾碌仲要係暴動<br />\n出返黎起碼26,7歲<span style=\"color: red;\">0工作經驗有案底<br />\n你自己諗</span></blockquote><br />\n有咩分別？"},{"pid":"5bc9df7bc64f5e1f34adcf5d894d56f47d08bf21","tid":158904,"uid":36359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T09:19:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>為公司或者自己公司既利益，激進人士未免就唔係太符合，因為一般我地認知既佢地都係將自己信念利益行先而唔係顧及或者保障公司利益為先，而其他既人仲話可以有個未知之數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以咁樣睇的話情願要翻普通人</blockquote><br />\n普通人都係自己利益行先 <br />\n冇糧出你仲番唔番工?"},{"pid":"7c95e2743781625e8896c537f058f3b714e6fe8d","tid":158904,"uid":71725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T09:20:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"873354e5ee840417b2e1fc53e6273620705b36bd","tid":158904,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T09:20:39.000Z","msg":"唔請<br />\n點解要請個有案底？"},{"pid":"d0c934d8cfd7acb7a99683fbc83e24ce8f1a1420","tid":158904,"uid":43842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T09:23:49.000Z","msg":"未必請。但一定叫佢黎in"},{"pid":"76a32574cce616ef6180165aa7035fe0513b28b5","tid":158904,"uid":28758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T09:24:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E8%B6%99%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E8%25B6%2599%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259B%2584&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK610Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=f85f4071\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E8%B6%99%